iROCK YOUR PARTY
ORLANDO WEDDING & EVENT DJS
MEET THE TEAM BEHIND THE DREAM
Hey there! We are the siblings behind iRock Your Party. We might look young to you, but we are all well seasoned in each of our event fields and make an awesome team. We have been involved in the industry for over 12 years and have always dreamed about combining our strengths and skills to create an entertainment company driven by passion, charisma, and attention to detail.
SEBASTIAN
Vision Director
Whether on the decks, the mic, or the lights, he’s the mastermind behind unforgettable parties. When it’s time to rock, Sebastian sets the vibe and brings the vision to life.
​
Sebastian@irockyourparty.com
​
SANTIAGO
Operations Manager
Santiago, as our Director of Operations, keeps the finances sharp, the logistics smooth, and the team in sync, making sure every event runs seamlessly from start to finish.
​
Santiago@irockyourparty.com
DANI
Marketing Specialist & Designer
Dani’s background in multimedia design and her photography expertise allow her to create dynamic visuals that capture the energy of our events. Whether designing, shooting, or editing, she makes sure iRock always looks as good as it feels.
​
Dani@irockyourparty.com

CORPORATE EVENTS DJ
iRock Your Party is a corporate events DJ company in Orlando, FL. While we typically serve the Central Florida region, including Tampa, St. Petersburg, Kissimmee, Winter Park, and Winter Garden, we travel worldwide!
Our corporate event DJs have been at conferences, summits, and parties all around the world. Let us rock your next event!
Contact us to turn your event into a reality.
​
Send us the information about your event and we will send
our complete corporate investment guide in less than 12 hours.

LIVE MUSICIANS FUSION SET
A  live musician and a DJ set brings the best of both worlds to your wedding, delivering a diverse and memorable experience that keeps the party going all night long, ensuring your special day is a hit from start to finish!
WHY CHOOSE iROCK ORLANDO DJS
We understand your wedding day should be one of the most magical and unforgettable days of your and your partner's life together. From planning to performance, our team has the industry experience, expertise, and empathy to know precisely how to ensure your wedding goes as expected. We have MC'd hundreds of Orlando weddings and will be honored to work with you.
​
...and they party rocked happily ever after
CONTACT US
RECEPTION PACKAGES
Elevate your event with a fusion of live musicians and a DJ. Customize your experience by adding multiple musicians or request our full band for an unforgettable performance. The price is per musician for a 2-hour set, assuming that iRock will be there to provide a sound system for the musician.
